Hierarchical List Demo
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>Using a heatmap control, you can represent or organize data into a hierarchical, tree-like structured data model. This structure allows the repetition of information by using parent-child representations. A parent can have many children but a child has only one parent. This sample demonstrates a hierarchical data model.</Paragraph>
